title: Maureen and Carlos Urrego – Remembranza
creator: Osvaldo Pugliese con Jorge Maciel
description:
Maureen and Carlos Urrego dance “Remembranza” by Osvaldo Pugliese, sung by Jorge Maciel, at the 3rd Southern California Tango Championship & Festival 2017 in Los Angeles, USA.
